OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHealth secretary defends   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdelay to social care cap   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The health secretary has defended the  
OL,6, delay to a cap on care costs in        
OL,7, England, saying it will allow more     
OL,8, funding for social care.               
OL,10,FUnder the plans people would have paid 
OL,11,Fno more than #86,000 towards their     
OL,12,Fpersonal care during their lifetime.   
OL,14,FSteve Barclay said the delay was a     
OL,15,F"difficult decision" but the government
OL,16,Fwas committed to the reforms.          
OL,18,FHe told the BBC the extra funding would
OL,19,Fhelp with discharging people from      
OL,20,Fhospitals more quickly.                
